title: Xperia Tipo Scarabeus ROM
description:
Xperia Tipo Scarabeus ROM

It is the best rom you've ever seen! Well it's a GAMING ROM so you can play with your favorite games without lags. I mixed Gimlo ROM (http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=2123835) and Paradox ROM (http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=2209026#taglist)

It contains:

-new statusbar with internet-speed meter
-Walkman ported for sony xperia tipo
-Based on FW 4.27
-Fully Deodexed and Zipaligned
-Infinite View
-Small Apps of Xperia Z
-Xperia Z Lockscreen(for Tipo)
-Theme of Xperia Z
-Google Ears
-Google Now Fully Working
-First Ever Gaming Rom
-JB keyboard
-Walkman and Acid audio
-Pre rooted
-CWM
-Highly Tweaked
-and Many More

Install: You need a rooted Xperia Tipo (how to root: http://scarabeustipo.blogspot.hu/)
And clockworkmod.

Install zips in order (you can choose between stock and orochy themes by the first zip, but install the #1 zip only once, with, or without orochy theme!)

Do it your own risk and I hope you like it!
